Isn't that a bit early?

352
00:29:47,081 --> 00:29:48,881
(頑張れ、私！)
(Do your best, me!)

353
00:29:49,081 --> 00:29:50,581
必要かもね
It might be necessary

354
00:29:50,581 --> 00:29:52,381
(今年こそは完食)
(this year for sure, eat it all)

355
00:29:52,481 --> 00:29:56,381
目指して頑張ります
I'll do my best aiming for that

356
00:30:00,293 --> 00:30:00,893
いいね
Nice.

357
00:30:00,993 --> 00:30:02,193
お願いは何？
What's your wish?

358
00:30:02,323 --> 00:30:03,743
ねえ、秘密だよ
Hey, it's a secret.

359
00:30:03,943 --> 00:30:05,993
おみくじなんて 気にしなくていいのに
You shouldn't worry about fortune slips.

360
00:30:06,193 --> 00:30:07,893
気合いが入ります
I'm getting fired up.

361
00:30:11,893 --> 00:30:15,193
君と初めての朝
My first morning with you.

362
00:30:15,693 --> 00:30:18,893
初日の出染まる君
You, colored by the first sunrise.

363
00:30:19,493 --> 00:30:22,493
オレンジ色輝いて
Shining in orange.

364
00:30:23,293 --> 00:30:24,093
ねえ ねえ
Hey, hey.

365
00:30:24,193 --> 00:30:25,893
触れていたいよ
I want to touch you.

366
00:30:26,493 --> 00:30:27,293
トントン
Knock knock.

367
00:30:27,393 --> 00:30:29,493
こっちおいで
Come over here.

368
00:30:29,893 --> 00:30:32,393
揺らしてよDJ パーティーナイト
Shake it, DJ, Party night!

369
00:30:33,393 --> 00:30:36,493
このままじゃ終われない
It can't end like this.

370
00:30:36,793 --> 00:30:39,993
今だけのチャンス 話そうよ
It's our only chance, let's talk.

371
00:30:41,293 --> 00:30:44,293
明日のことは忘れよう
Let's forget about tomorrow.

372
00:30:44,593 --> 00:30:47,593
今じゃなきゃダメなんです
It has to be now.

373
00:30:47,993 --> 00:30:51,093
急展開を楽しもう
Let's enjoy the sudden turn of events.

374
00:30:51,393 --> 00:30:54,393
今日こそは君に
Today, for sure, to you...

375
00:30:54,693 --> 00:30:57,093
好きだよ
I love you.

376
00:31:10,793 --> 00:31:21,593
Oh oh oh... 君じゃなきゃダメなんです
Oh oh oh... It has to be you.

377
00:31:21,893 --> 00:31:24,493
Oh oh oh...

378
00:31:25,193 --> 00:31:28,193
Please please こっちおいで
Please please, come here.

379
00:31:28,593 --> 00:31:31,293
あげてこうぜDJ パーティーナイト
Turn it up, DJ, Party night!

380
00:31:32,493 --> 00:31:35,393
淋しいなんて言ってない
I'm not saying I'm lonely.

381
00:31:35,793 --> 00:31:39,193
嫌なことはポイさわごう
Throw away the bad stuff, let's party!

382
00:31:40,093 --> 00:31:43,093
大好きな人と踊ろう
Let's dance with the one we love.

383
00:31:43,393 --> 00:31:46,493
大胆なことしちゃおう
Let's do something bold.

384
00:31:46,793 --> 00:31:50,093
急接近は雨上がり
Getting close after the rain.

385
00:31:50,393 --> 00:31:53,493
今日こそは君に伝える
Today, for sure, I'll tell you.

386
00:31:53,693 --> 00:31:56,093
好きだよ
I love you.

387
00:32:46,593 --> 00:32:50,093
気まぐれロマンティック
Kimagure Romantic

388
00:32:59,093 --> 00:33:02,193
ロマンティック 恋のアンテナは
Romantic, the antenna of love...

389
00:33:03,993 --> 00:33:07,493
嵐でどこかへ飛んでいった
...was blown away somewhere by the storm.

390
00:33:09,993 --> 00:33:13,293
嘘でしょ 冷たく知らんぷり
You're kidding, right? Acting cold and indifferent.

391
00:33:14,993 --> 00:33:18,593
こしゃくなエクボにちょっと
That cheeky dimple...

392
00:33:18,693 --> 00:33:20,993
心が揺れてる
...is making my heart flutter a bit.

393
00:33:21,893 --> 00:33:25,793
本当は本気で私を
Honestly, I want you to...

394
00:33:26,993 --> 00:33:30,593
叱ってくれる大事な人
...be that special someone who'll truly scold me.

395
00:33:32,493 --> 00:33:36,193
なんて言ったらあいつは
If I said that, he would...

396
00:33:37,393 --> 00:33:41,093
得意げになるから
...just get all full of himself,

397
00:33:41,193 --> 00:33:43,793
もう褒めたりしない
so I won't praise him anymore.

398
00:33:44,293 --> 00:33:47,893
退屈な運命に飽き飽きしたの
I'm fed up with this boring fate.

399
00:33:49,293 --> 00:33:55,793
知らない言葉で解き放して
Set me free with words I've never heard before.

400
00:33:55,993 --> 00:33:59,993
ねだりだり心の扉を壊してよ
I'm begging you, break down the door to my heart.

401
00:34:02,193 --> 00:34:07,493
大切なことは目を見て言って
Look me in the eye when you say what's important.

402
00:34:07,893 --> 00:34:13,093
あなたとならこの街を抜け出せる
With you, I can escape this city.

403
00:34:13,993 --> 00:34:19,493
今すぐ連れ出して My Sweet Sweet Darling
Take me away right now, my sweet, sweet darling.

404
00:34:31,993 --> 00:34:36,593
ドラマティック 笑顔の秘密を
Dramatic, the secret of that smile...

405
00:34:37,693 --> 00:34:41,193
誰だって探し続けてる
...is what everyone keeps searching for.

406
00:34:43,393 --> 00:34:46,893
見上げた空に描くの
I'll paint on the sky I look up at...

407
00:34:47,493 --> 00:34:49,993
幸せの形
...the shape of happiness.

408
00:34:50,593 --> 00:34:54,093
そう 私らしくいたい
Yes, I want to stay true to myself.

409
00:34:54,893 --> 00:34:59,393
気まぐれなテンションで振り回すけど
I might lead you around with my whimsical moods, but...

410
00:35:00,105 --> 00:35:06,105
★気まぐれロマンティック★
★Kimagure Romantic★

411
00:35:00,105 --> 00:35:06,285
この手はかならず離さないで
Don't ever let go of this hand.

412
00:35:06,385 --> 00:35:08,515
ねぇ
Hey.

413
00:35:08,615 --> 00:35:12,855
ダーリン ダーリン 心の扉を叩いてよ
Darling, darling, knock on the door of my heart.

414
00:35:12,955 --> 00:35:18,435
素直な気持ちがあふれてゆく
My honest feelings are overflowing.

415
00:35:18,535 --> 00:35:23,815
あなたとならば笑っていられるよ
With you, I can keep on smiling.

416
00:35:23,915 --> 00:35:29,555
今すぐ駆け出すの my sweet sweet darling
I'm running out right now, my sweet sweet darling.

417
00:35:41,625 --> 00:35:47,005
ダーリン ダーリン きっと私はつかめるよ
Darling, darling, I'm sure I can grasp it.

418
00:35:47,105 --> 00:35:52,505
幸せの意味に気づいてゆく
I'm starting to realize the meaning of happiness.

419
00:35:52,605 --> 00:35:57,805
あなたとならば明日を変えられる
With you, I can change tomorrow.

420
00:35:57,905 --> 00:36:03,505
今すぐ連れ出して my sweet sweet darling
Take me away right now, my sweet sweet darling.

421
00:36:03,605 --> 00:36:08,805
ダーリン ダーリン 心の扉を壊してよ
Darling, darling, break down the door of my heart.

422
00:36:08,905 --> 00:36:14,305
大切なことは目を見て言って
Tell me the important things while looking into my eyes.

423
00:36:14,405 --> 00:36:21,005
あなたとならばこの街を抜け出せる
With you, I can escape this town.

424
00:36:21,105 --> 00:36:27,305
今すぐ連れ出して my sweet sweet darling
Take me away right now, my sweet sweet darling.

425
00:37:00,705 --> 00:37:07,555
探しに行くんだ　そこへ
I'm going to find it, over there.

426
00:37:08,105 --> 00:37:15,105
春擬き
