Harumodoki
Lyrics: Yanaginagi / Composition: Katsutoshi Kitagawa

427
00:37:19,305 --> 00:37:24,405
空欄を埋め　完成した定理
Filling in the blanks, the completed theorem.

428
00:37:24,505 --> 00:37:29,905
正しいはずなのに　ひらり空回り
It should be correct, but it's just spinning in circles.

429
00:37:30,305 --> 00:37:35,355
未来はいびつで　わずかな亀裂から
The future is distorted, and from a small crack...

430
00:37:35,455 --> 00:37:40,905
いくらでもよれて　理想から逸れていくんだ
...it twists and turns, deviating from the ideal.

431
00:37:41,705 --> 00:37:46,955
ぬるま湯が　すうっと冷めていく音がしてた
I heard the sound of lukewarm water quickly cooling down.

432
00:37:47,105 --> 00:37:52,405
道を変えるのなら
If I'm to change my path...

433
00:37:52,405 --> 00:37:57,205
のなら
...if so...

434
00:37:59,955 --> 00:38:05,505
今なら　こんなレプリカはいらない
Right now, I don't need a replica like this.

435
00:38:05,505 --> 00:38:10,955
本物と呼べるものだけでいい
Only something that can be called "genuine" is enough.

436
00:38:11,305 --> 00:38:16,955
探しに行くんだ　そこへ
I'm going to find it, over there.

437
00:38:16,955 --> 00:38:24,905
でもそれは良く出来たフェアリーテイルみたい
But it's like a well-crafted fairy tale.

438
00:38:33,505 --> 00:38:38,705
答えの消えた　空欄を見つめる
I stare at the blanks where the answers have vanished.

439
00:38:38,705 --> 00:38:44,305
埋めたはずなのに　どうしても分からない
I should have filled them in, but I just don't understand.

440
00:38:44,505 --> 00:38:49,705
綺麗な花は　大事に育てても
Even if I carefully raise beautiful flowers...

441
00:38:49,705 --> 00:38:55,305
遠慮ない土足で　簡単に踏みにじられた
...they were easily trampled by unreserved muddy feet.

442
00:38:55,705 --> 00:39:01,105
降り積もる白に　小さな芽覆われていく
The small buds are being covered by the piling white snow.

443
00:39:01,305 --> 00:39:06,605
遠い遠い春は
The far, far away spring...

444
00:39:06,605 --> 00:39:14,405
息の下
...is beneath the breath.

445
00:39:14,605 --> 00:39:20,105
見えないものはどうして　記憶から薄れてしまうんだ
Why do things that can't be seen fade away from memory?

446
00:39:20,105 --> 00:39:25,605
探しに行く場所さえも
Even the place I'm going to find...

447
00:39:25,605 --> 00:39:30,905
見失う僕たちは　気付かず芽を踏む
...is lost to us as we unknowingly tread on the buds.

448
00:39:38,305 --> 00:39:47,405
思い出を頼りに　救ってた花はすぐ枯れた
The flower I saved by relying on memories withered quickly.

449
00:39:48,605 --> 00:39:54,105
足元には　気付かずに　気付かずに
At my feet, without noticing, without noticing...

450
00:40:04,717 --> 00:40:07,717
本物と呼べる場所を
A place I can call real...

451
00:40:07,717 --> 00:40:11,917
（場所を）
(...a place)

452
00:40:15,617 --> 00:40:18,517
探しに行くのはきっと
I'm sure that searching for it...

453
00:40:18,517 --> 00:40:22,617
（きっと）
(...I'm sure)

454
00:40:26,617 --> 00:40:30,317
今なんだ　こんなレプリカはいらない
It's now. I don't need a replica like this.

455
00:40:30,317 --> 00:40:37,417
本物と呼べるものだけでいい
Only things I can call real are enough.

456
00:40:37,417 --> 00:40:43,117
探しに行くから　君を
Because I'm going to find you...

457
00:40:43,117 --> 00:40:48,517
ありがとう　小さな目　見つけてくれたこと
Thank you, for those small eyes finding me.

458
00:40:50,117 --> 00:40:54,117
君は呟いた
...you muttered.

459
00:41:38,317 --> 00:41:43,717
24時間くらい　あれいいのにな
I wish I had about 24 hours...

460
00:41:43,717 --> 00:41:48,117
やり残したことたくさんで　鞄がパンパン
So many things left undone, my bag is bursting.

461
00:41:48,117 --> 00:41:50,117
君をわかりたい
I want to understand you.

462
00:41:50,117 --> 00:41:51,917
君を忘れたい
I want to forget you.

463
00:41:51,917 --> 00:41:53,917
君を守りたい
I want to protect you.

464
00:41:53,917 --> 00:41:57,117
それぞれの願い
Each of our wishes.

465
00:42:00,117 --> 00:42:01,417
海の家！
Beach house!

466
00:42:01,417 --> 00:42:02,817
山の家！
Mountain house!

467
00:42:02,817 --> 00:42:04,317
故郷の家！
Hometown home!

468
00:42:04,317 --> 00:42:07,517
世界周遊　悠久休暇
World tour, eternal vacation.

469
00:42:07,517 --> 00:42:09,217
お天道様を飲み干して
Drink up the sun...

470
00:42:09,217 --> 00:42:11,117
いっせーのーせでもぐり込め
...and dive in on the count of three.

471
00:42:11,117 --> 00:42:13,117
誰ひとり欠けず川をさかのぼれ
Follow the river upstream with no one left behind.

472
00:42:13,117 --> 00:42:15,417
弾む息継ぎ仲間の声
Bouncing breaths, the voices of friends.

473
00:42:15,417 --> 00:42:18,317
踊る　止まらないこの水流と
Dancing with this unstoppable current...

474
00:42:18,317 --> 00:42:20,417
泳いで勝って大丈夫
...swimming and winning, it's okay.

475
00:42:20,417 --> 00:42:23,317
どんなつまずきだって　きっとすべての夏が微笑んで
No matter the stumble, surely every summer will smile.

476
00:42:23,317 --> 00:42:27,117
あんなに早く大人になりたかったのに
I wanted to grow up so fast back then...

477
00:42:27,117 --> 00:42:29,417
そうだろ
Right?

478
00:42:29,417 --> 00:42:30,117
そうだろ
Right?

479
00:42:30,117 --> 00:42:31,117
そうだろ
Right?

480
00:42:31,117 --> 00:42:33,117
わかんないよ
I don't know.

481
00:42:33,117 --> 00:42:34,517
永遠なんてないさ
Nothing lasts forever,

482
00:42:34,517 --> 00:42:36,517
夏休みだって
not even summer vacation.

483
00:42:36,517 --> 00:42:39,617
数週間煌めき　またひとつの物語
A few weeks of sparkle, another story begins.

484
00:42:39,617 --> 00:42:41,117
まだ納得いかないさ
I'm still not convinced,

485
00:42:41,117 --> 00:42:43,117
油蝉だって
even the cicadas...

486
00:42:43,117 --> 00:42:46,117
3年も持ちこがれて　飛び出したお祭り
...wait for three years for this festival to burst out.

487
00:42:46,117 --> 00:42:50,117
潮風に溶けて　夏に木霊した
Dissolving in the sea breeze, echoing in the summer.

488
00:42:50,117 --> 00:42:54,517
僕らのササマバケーション
Our Sasama Vacation.

489
00:42:55,417 --> 00:42:56,917
海の家！
Beach house!

490
00:42:56,917 --> 00:42:58,417
山の家！
Mountain house!

491
00:42:58,417 --> 00:42:59,917
故郷の家！
Hometown home!

492
00:42:59,917 --> 00:43:03,117
世界周遊　悠久休暇
World tour, eternal vacation.

493
00:43:03,517 --> 00:43:06,317
僕が好きな君が好きなやつは誰が好きなんだい？
Who does the person you like, that I like, like?

494
00:43:06,317 --> 00:43:07,917
多角関係！
Polygonal relationship!

495
00:43:07,917 --> 00:43:11,317
あれあれ何遍転生したって待って何遍？
Hey, hey, no matter how many times I reincarnate—wait, how many?

496
00:43:11,317 --> 00:43:14,617
我々惹かれ合う　海よりも遠い僕らの住処も
We're drawn to each other, even our homes further than the sea...

497
00:43:14,617 --> 00:43:18,617
また時が巡れば思い出すよ　あの青と青の境界線を
When time comes around again, I'll remember that boundary between blue and blue.

498
00:43:18,617 --> 00:43:22,617
皿際覗いて白く雲を
Peeking at the edge of the plate, the white clouds...

499
00:43:22,617 --> 00:43:26,617
来年も再来年も　笑って泣いてみたいなぁ
Next year and the year after, I want to laugh and cry.

500
00:43:26,617 --> 00:43:27,617
お前も！
You!

501
00:43:27,617 --> 00:43:28,617
お供！
Companion!

502
00:43:28,617 --> 00:43:29,617
君も！
You too!

503
00:43:29,617 --> 00:43:31,117
大好きだ！
I love you all!

504
00:43:31,117 --> 00:43:32,517
永遠なんてないさ
Nothing lasts forever,

505
00:43:32,517 --> 00:43:34,117
花火玉だって
not even fireworks.

506
00:43:34,117 --> 00:43:37,117
数秒間煌めき　命燃やす向日葵
Sparkling for a few seconds, sunflowers burning their lives.

507
00:43:37,117 --> 00:43:38,517
まだ納得いかないさ
I'm still not convinced,

508
00:43:38,517 --> 00:43:40,117
学生服だって
even school uniforms...

509
00:43:40,117 --> 00:43:44,317
3年玉送り育ち　押し入れの片隅
...three years of growth, now in a corner of the closet.

510
00:43:44,317 --> 00:43:47,417
共に今　この川下ろう
Let's go down this river together now.

511
00:43:47,417 --> 00:43:51,417
本当はみんな　気づかないふりしてた
Actually, everyone was just pretending not to notice.

512
00:43:51,417 --> 00:44:00,117
この夏には　もう二度と戻れないってことを
That we can never return to this summer again.

513
00:44:00,117 --> 00:44:03,617
24時間くらい　あれいいのにな
I wish I had about 24 hours...

514
00:44:03,617 --> 00:44:07,517
波待ちしたことたくさんで　鞄がパンパン
So many times waiting for waves, my bag is bursting.

515
00:44:07,517 --> 00:44:09,217
君を泣かせない
I won't make you cry.

516
00:44:09,217 --> 00:44:10,917
君を忘れない
I won't forget you.

517
00:44:10,917 --> 00:44:13,217
君を離さない
I won't let you go.

518
00:44:13,217 --> 00:44:16,317
それぞれの誓い
Each of our oaths.

519
00:44:16,317 --> 00:44:22,617
沈む日と共に　水平線に隠した
Hidden in the horizon along with the setting sun.

520
00:44:22,617 --> 00:44:26,617
