Dissolving in the sea breeze, echoing in the summer.

526
00:44:51,617 --> 00:44:55,417
僕らのササマバケーション
Our Sasama Vacation.

527
00:44:55,417 --> 00:44:58,317
元気してるかー？
How are you doing?

528
00:44:58,317 --> 00:45:00,116
ごはん食べれてるー？
Are you eating well?

529
00:45:00,629 --> 00:45:01,729
恋してるぞ！
I love you guys!

530
00:45:04,029 --> 00:45:05,229
その夏は一度きりだ
That summer only happens once

531
00:45:05,229 --> 00:45:07,229
